  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK530">
<l>uḻaippirintu kāraṇattiṉ vantāṉai vēnta</l>
<l>ṉiḻaittirun teṇṇik koḷal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When one may have left him, and for some cause has returned to him, let the king fulfil the object (for which he has come back) and thoughtfully receive him again.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
